      (I)求$\omega$的值\\
      (II)设$\alpha,\beta\in\Bigl[0,\dfrac{\piup}2\Bigr]$，$f{\Bigl(5\alpha+\dfrac{5\piup}3\Bigr)}=-\dfrac{6}5$，$f{\Bigl(5\beta-\dfrac{5\piup}6\Bigr)}=\dfrac{16}{17}$，求$\cos{(\alpha+\beta)}$的值.
      \begin{answer}
