        (II)$\sin\alpha=\dfrac{3}5$，$\cos\beta=\dfrac{8}{17}$，$\cos\alpha=\dfrac{4}5$，$\sin\beta=\dfrac{15}{17}$，$\cos{(\alpha+\beta)}=-\dfrac{13}{85}$.
      \end{answer}
